7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"b1a702390c9be8302c3d0feecaf0d11cd00ded44","tid":1672823,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a768ccb212235b858d0830a05d8a34ddd38d1f1d","tid":1672823,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9b5ed44a7108eb7e805aa1ff43ab2410ca059426","tid":1672823,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"貼紙係咪連登豬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edd319cf48dbc0115a49094c1acf1b9da9e5447","tid":1672823,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0952b246493a29e0cb06c20be2baa124a37205a2","tid":1672823,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈第一步最緊要就係張貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 